<F P=100> West Europe </F>
<H3> <TI>   Defense University Delegation Leaves for Portugal </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW2502044094 Beijing XINHUA in English 0425 GMT 25 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW2502044094 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>


<TEXT>
