<F P=103> OW2202095594 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, February 22 (XINHUA) -- Chinese 
Vice-President Rong Yiren met with Enrique V. Iglesias, 
president of the Inter-American Development Bank (IDB), and his 
party here today. 
  Rong briefed the guests on China's economic development 
since 
the country launched its reform and opening-up more than a 
decade ago and particularly in recent years. 
  Iglesias expressed appreciation of China's great 
achievements 
in the past 15 years and voiced the hope that the economic and 
trade ties between China and the Latin American countries would 
