<H3> <TI>   U.S. Assistant Secretary Shattuck Leaves for China </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW2602051094 Beijing XINHUA in English 0455 GMT 26 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW2602051094 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>


