Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Washington, February 25 (XINHUA) -- U.S. Assistant 
Secretary of State John Shattuck left here today for a week-long 
visit to China. 
  The purpose of Shattuck's trip is to pave the way for a 
visit 
to Beijing in mid-March by Secretary of State Warren 
