<F P=102>  BK3101065594 Quezon City PTV-4 Television Network in Tagalog 
0500 GMT 31 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK3101065594 </F>
<F P=104>  Quezon City PTV-4 Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Tagalog </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Moro National Liberation Front [MNLF] will 
respect the authority of officials of the Autonomous Region in 
Muslim Mindanao [ARMM]. This was the assurance given by MNLF 
Chairman Nur Misuari to Senator Santanina Rasul during their 
dialogue earlier. 
  The apprehension that the term of office of ARMM officials 
would be affected stemmed from Misuari's call for the 
establishment of a provisional government in Mindanao. ARMM 
officials, headed by the regional governor, have a three-year 
term of office. 

