<F P=104>  Hanoi VNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Hanoi VNA Jan. 31 -- The Vietnam-Romania 
Intergovernmental Committee for Economic, Scientific and 
Technological Cooperation held its 14th session here this 
morning. 
  Present at the meeting were, on the Vietnamese side, Mr Le 
Van Triet, minister of trade, chairman of Vietnam's 
sub-committee and other members of the Vietnamese Government's 
economic delegation and on the Romanian side, Mr. Cristian 
Ioneseu, minister of trade, chairman of the Romania's 
