implementation 
of economic-commercial, scientific and technological cooperation 
between the two countries over the past time and discussed 
cooperation programme for the 1994-1995 period. Reports on the 
preparation of documents namely agreement on investment 
encouragement and protection, agreement on double tax avoidance 
and documents on the committee's organization and statute were 
presented at the meeting. 
  Other relating matters including the settlement of debt by 
convertible ruble, next session's agenda and time, etc. were 
also discussed at the meeting. 

