  [Text] The officials of the Autonomous Region for Muslim 
Mindanao [ARMM] will not be dismissed from their posts in 
connection with the ongoing peace talks. This assurance was 
given by Nur Misuari, chairman of the Moro National Liberation 
Front [MNLF], to Senator Santanina Rasul, chair of Senate 
